    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Small muffs or fingerless mittens that cover the wrist and part of the hand. Most often these are knitted or crocheted. For handwear with finger holes, use 'mitts (fingerless handwear)'. </Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
